{"tid":1311073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉淑儀建議林鄭月娥「快閃落區」","createTime":"2019-07-13T04:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T04:31:31.000Z","uid":277072,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2da5784ae241ffed9208181d8805d183886a2f","tid":1311073,"uid":277072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:09:34.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀說，對於近期社會事件感到痛心，形容現時社會秩序崩潰。她認為，行政長官林鄭月娥應該多落區，雖然有可能被包圍，但可以考慮「快閃落區」，若一直留在禮賓府，只會予人感覺疏離。她希望政府以理服人，對於不能回應的訴求應該大聲及主動解釋。 <br />\n<br />\nsource: RTHK<br />\n<br />\n依兩姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6027027db9674f634c493f5d106cd2a3ed7f6f","tid":1311073,"uid":65790,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"一落即圍<br />\n過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2600185641a1feaca53a2916b68ef867cfdd0c4","tid":1311073,"uid":68509,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"姐姐又醒d絕世好橋畀妹妹喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e760e327ec81a89451c25543284aa651229ed19d","tid":1311073,"uid":55162,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"姐姐真係好人<br />\n成日教精妹妹"},{"pid":"1f82cd0a8a0ceecc301857deaca98db57712de20","tid":1311073,"uid":173849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"咁大仇口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />口"},{"pid":"65846fb081a0fb1e4392c0cba87450355348f113","tid":1311073,"uid":33674,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:18:07.000Z","msg":"你夠膽行入任何一個大型屋苑，執返條命仔行返出嚟，我支持你終身做特首！"},{"pid":"eac460e3b6f2ed07ef17138a166a65228a7a11e2","tid":1311073,"uid":997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:19:00.